name: War is Heck
description: What is this?! We're in war, soldier, and you're spending your time reading? What use is reading when you're scooching your skinny butt through rat-infested mud in the middle of a hurricane under live fire? None, that's what! Now get in formation!

skinlines.name: Commando
skinlines.description: Just your average bottomless pit of scum and villainy. Bosses vie for power; pacts are made and broken; friendships meet their end on the edge of twisted, subtle knives. And yet, there's something more to this city. Something undiscovered, imperceptible. Something... infinite.

skinlines.name: Omega Squad
skinlines.description: When the war came, Omega Squad was sent to end it. Now only one of them remains, a yordle with no battles left to fight but his own...
